1. *Reči* o njegovom uspehu su se proširile po celom gradu. (The news of his success spread throughout the city.)

2. Njegove *reči* su joj dale snagu da nastavi. (His words gave her the strength to continue.)

3. *Reči* su bile suviše slatke da bi bile istinite. (The words were too sweet to be true.)

4. Ona je ponovo slušala *reči* iz njegovih usana. (She heard the words from his lips again.)

5. Svi smo se začudili njegovim *rečima*. (We all were surprised by his words.)

6. Slušajući njegove *reči*, shvatila je svoju grešku. (Listening to his words, she realized her mistake.)